","4 medium eggs"]}],"id":"r365466","imageLink":"https:\/\/4.bp.blogspot.com\/-GvhD1FmCO0A\/XZVRjjUljQI\/AAAAAAAAdQA\/Z9eePYTiJZ4vpeg1ACYVPMvAh_qw_jx3wCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_r-4_ixdilaGxJ7rR.png","title":"Pizza with Red Pepper Sauce, Spinach and Eggs","publishedAt":"2019-03-09T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19.4 g","fat":"20.6 g","uom":"per 1 portions","carbohydrates":"39.6 g","calories":"1765 kJ \/ 422 kcal"},"usefulItems":"large bowl, cling film, rolling pin, large baking trays, oven","hintsAndTricks":["Dough, tomato sauce and grated cheese are all easily prepared in minutes in your Thermomix®. There are many pizzas on Cookidoo® topped with meat or fish, as well as gluten-free versions for those on special diets.","You can substitute spinach and eggs with almost anything you have in the fridge (e.g. ham, salami, mushrooms, mixed peppers, courgette, olives)."],"basicInfo":["easy","25m","1h 45m","8 portions"]}